<p>

<b>Roger Michell</b> (<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../820/15820.xml">
June 5</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../672/34672.xml">
1956</link>) is an <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../316/9316.xml">
English</link></country>
 <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref> theatre, television and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../181/506181.xml">
film director</link>. </p>

<sec>
<st>
Personal life</st>

<p>

He was born in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../002/25002.xml">
Pretoria</link> but spent significant parts of his childhood in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../428/37428.xml">
